'Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.79,0:22:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,所以我再也不會放手了
'Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.86,0:22:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,如果放手的話 還不如一起掉下去
'Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.17,0:22:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,我也是從那時起對你念念不忘的
'Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,但是…誰去保護那些孩子呢
'Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:22:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,只有靠你了
'Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:23:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,那些孩子的未來只有靠你來拯救了
'Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,但是…但是…
'Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
'Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.13,0:23:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,力量 最終章
'Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.63,0:23:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,拜託了 救救我們





Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.31,0:00:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是在此沉睡了千年的音律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,古代的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,守衛拼死地抵抗超乎了我的想像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,讓我吃盡苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村長盡給我搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.95,0:00:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我浪費了不少時間才收集到這音律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊村子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我讓這傢伙幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.11,0:01:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了奪回失去的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.86,0:01:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了那麼多苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查明了這裡的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬上了鎮長的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發掘出埋藏的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後騙取你們的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快告訴我剩下的音律在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.61,0:01:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拷問實在太浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實交待就讓你死得痛快點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.46,0:01:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 還是直接殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用穢土轉生來逼供吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你真了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你打敗了曉的佩因
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我都敗給他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我失去了力量 即便如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的陳年舊帳我沒興趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢對大叔下手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些蛇會吞噬查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你越是增加查克拉量束縛得就越緊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還如此狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當自己是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…這個就是你們想要的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了多克老師和鳴人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來音律在孩子們的手裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經在上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是鼓起勇氣來救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜 應該是分身…還有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是五個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪不在家…為什麼來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之小心前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 別碰孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湊齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於湊齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湊齊七根了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能恢復力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉…吞噬…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若想控制力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可用七段音律組合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照規定順序啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:06:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組合不同 力量釋放的強弱亦不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手動操作可更新音律的輸入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦或七個時辰自動感知並更新
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音律組合若不合規定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,則保持更新前的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這是對的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼如此亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見…老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 厲害 真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…天之矛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這就是啟動的順序…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼釋放力量就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野心太強會自取滅亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這絕非人類可掌控之物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確認過以前的通緝令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經以為你喪生於曉的戰鬥裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅長通靈術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著上千條人命在手的殺人狂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還與大蛇丸一起研究禁術穢土轉生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束手就擒吧 迪索納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下你們全完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井野 丁次…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好感受藝術的魅力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝術就是…爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙要進行儀式…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須先寫咒印才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們決不能讓他有機可乘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…到底是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的…力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迄今為止…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從很多人身上學到很多重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個很厲害的人教會了我很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕非螺旋丸 仙術或是九尾的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穢土轉生的忍者竟然沒有復活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來被當作棄子了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於逮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的能力 沒人協助是無法發揮的 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怪就怪你那冗長複雜的準備過程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,協助 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個會給人添麻煩的老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不會再讓你亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能就此放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這算什麼啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來組成你的克隆蛇有很大缺陷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力求快速成長的同時壽命卻變短了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為防萬一 我還準備了二十多個對策呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來用不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在不斷崩解墜落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的地面是由樹根支撐的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕緊從巨坑脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 那個無法阻止嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股籠罩世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會毀滅世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能沐浴在那股力量之下…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,想要守護 想要幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,最重要的人們 我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.82,0:22:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,相信正義的力量 相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.54,0:22:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:22:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,力量 最終章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,這次的禮物是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.68,0:23:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,在明信片上寫下必須事項和尺碼寄往以上地址
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,將抽取40名幸運觀眾發放獎品
